====== Difficult Terrain

Move at half speed -- moving 1 foot costs 2 feet of speed.

===== Special Types of Movement

====== Climbing, Swimming, and Crawling

Each foot of movement costs 1 extra foot (2 extra feet in difficult terrain). You ignore this if you have and use a relevant speed (e.g. climbing or swimming speed). At the DM's option this may require a successful Strength (Athletics) check.